_at":"2026-05-05T18:27:55Z","updated_at":"2026-05-06T11:17:42Z","closed_at":"2026-05-06T08:10:33Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### What happened?\n\n### Description\nFor countries where Commerce Guys rules apply that Locality is unused, Commerce appears to discard any submitted data from address forms for Locality. \n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n1. Submit a shipping or billing address for a country where this applied (UAE for example). Post a Locality (can be the same as Administrative Area in most cases)\n2. Look at the processed address, either in Commerce or the address row in DB. See that Locality was discarded.\n\n### Expected behavior\nEven if a field is not used in a valid address based on a region, with Commerce Guys rules, that field value should be retained. \n\n\n### Actual behavior\nField values for unused fields, based on Commerce Guys rules validations, are discarded. \n\n### Craft CMS version\n\nCraft Pro 5.9.20\n\n### Craft Commerce version\n\n5.6.2\n\n### PHP version\n\n8.3.28\n\n### Operating system and version\n\nLinux 6.8.0-90-generic\n\n### Database type and version\n\nMySQL 8.0.45\n\n### Image driver and version\n\nImagick 3.8.0 (ImageMagick 6.9.12-98)\n\n### Installed plugins and versions\n\n<img width=\"1450\" height=\"1016\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c0756e68-0fc7-4c01-98c8-072a447fba9d\" />","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/craftcms/commerce/issues/4296/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/craftcms/commerce/issues/4296/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":